{"tid":2282600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞協盃金球] [波台雷動] 今次到林嘉緯啦","createTime":"2020-11-12T03:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T08:05:14.000Z","uid":19847,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"423552c15901a212a45f05aa6df4bfa08c30584d","tid":2282600,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>亞協盃金球選舉八強 AFC Cup Bracket Challenge Quarter-Final</strong></span><br />\n今次投林嘉緯呀🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\n呢球係嘉緯喺2014年亞協盃十六強<br />\n傑志對印尼球隊阿雷馬嘅入波<br />\n最後賽果係傑志 2-0 阿雷馬<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>14/11 16:00截止</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9Yz7tH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9Yz7tH.jpg&h=3f374944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入波片段喺投票link入面<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>投票link:</strong></span> <a href=\"https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/latest/news/bracket-challenge-quarter-final-safawi-rasid-jdt-vs-lam-ka-wai-kitchee-sc?fbclid=IwAR2NdkN3T_5Vmp3n76eoBJWtrvkml3b5XjyaaBQ4W7oDaXZBfdfRko1f0XU[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-afc.com%2Fcompetitions%2Fafc-cup%2Flatest%2Fnews%2Fbracket-challenge-quarter-final-safawi-rasid-jdt-vs-lam-ka-wai-kitchee-sc%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2NdkN3T_5Vmp3n76eoBJWtrvkml3b5XjyaaBQ4W7oDaXZBfdfRko1f0XU%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Auz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=55704153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/latest/news/bracket-challenge-quarter-final-safawi-rasid-jdt-vs-lam-ka-wai-kitchee-sc?fbclid=IwAR2NdkN3T_5Vmp3n76eoBJWtrvkml3b5XjyaaBQ4W7oDaXZBfdfRko1f0XU[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"5090d8c12ada5c473a9fb53282764a5c3c9c141f","tid":2282600,"uid":19847,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"另外想講下個人點看待呢類投票<br />\n我見有人會因為對家嗰球靚d<br />\n而唔投比香港代表<br />\n其實呢類純玩動員能力既投票<br />\n應該更加着重可以帶黎既影響<br />\n<br />\n兩年前亞冠<br />\n鄭展龍拎左每週同年度金球<br />\n對內<br />\n鄭展龍/傑志/香港足球因為正面原因<br />\n喺本地媒體曝光多兩次<br />\n電視都有報導<br />\n對外<br />\n鄭展龍本人可以喺AFC網站有個簡短訪問<br />\n而AFC社交媒體喺疫情期間都有翻炒<br />\n<br />\n一切只係緣於大家認真對待呢d投票<br />\n一味話香港足球無得救<br />\n係於事無補<br />\n我相信每人既細微舉動<br />\n都可以為香港足球帶黎影響<br />\nFrom: 數字球"},{"pid":"76721fe3f2a817edf6d43b73050c30630395531e","tid":2282600,"uid":19847,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"其實成件事好簡單姐<br />\n入去投票網站<br />\n碌落去揀返&rsquo;Chan Siu Ki&rsquo;就搞掂<br />\n仲可以重複投票<br />\n(約兩分鐘投一次票先算數，太快會DQ票)<br />\n<br />\n一部電話每次係可以投15票up<br />\nSafari<br />\nSafari無痕<br />\nChrome<br />\nChrome無痕<br />\nFirefox<br />\nFirefox無痕<br />\nOpera<br />\nOpera無痕<br />\nFacebook 內置browser<br />\nIG 內置browser<br />\nTG 內置browser<br />\nTwitter 內置browser<br />\n連登內置browser<br />\nFb Messenger 內置browser<br />\nSkype 內置browser<br />\n<br />\n我真係諗唔明點解會輸<br />\n可唔可以幫手贏一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFrom: 會然鼠B"},{"pid":"af92cf5a3b0ecc27e00cd67515af7816c907ce56","tid":2282600,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成件事好簡單姐<br />\n入去投票網站<br />\n碌落去揀返&rsquo;Lam Ka Wai&rsquo;就搞掂<br />\n仲可以重複投票<br />\n(約兩分鐘投一次票先算數，太快會DQ票)<br />\n<br />\n一部電話每次係可以投15票up<br />\nSafari<br />\nSafari無痕<br />\nChrome<br />\nChrome無痕<br />\nFirefox<br />\nFirefox無痕<br />\nOpera<br />\nOpera無痕<br />\nFacebook 內置browser<br />\nIG 內置browser<br />\nTG 內置browser<br />\nTwitter 內置browser<br />\n連登內置browser<br />\nFb Messenger 內置browser<br />\nSkype 內置browser<br />\n<br />\n我真係諗唔明點解會輸<br />\n可唔可以幫手贏一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face